data.description: Charming 3-Bedroom on Indy's west side! Located on a no-through street, this home offers a large, private fenced-in yard with a spacious front porch and rear covered patio, and a large driveway leading to a 2-car detached garage. Enjoy multiple flex spaces, including one on the main floor and the loft on the upper, and an enormous mud room. Great rental property opportunity! Roof - 2017, Water Heater - 2022, AC - 2017
